snippet.title: Uri Attack: CM Mehbooba Mufti Pays Tribute to Martyrs

localized.description:
Uri Attack: Jammu and Kashmir Chief Minister Mehbooba Mufti pays tribute to martyrs. Four Pakistani suicide terrorists attacked the army camp and killed seventeen unarmed Indian soldiers. 
Watch how an Indian BSF jawan challenge these terrorists and killed on of them before martyrdom. Security forces suspect Sipah-e-Sahaba Pakistan (SSP) is behind the attack. SSP operates under Jaish-e-Mohammad chief Masood Azhar.
